      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Implementation Plan",
      "position": {
        "x": 360,
        "y": 540
      },
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 260,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Suggested Sequence\n\n## Phase 1\n- define first-class intent verbs\n- define layout responsibility boundaries\n- identify low-risk assisted actions\n\n## Phase 2\n- prototype one-click authoring flows\n- validate how much geometry can safely be system-owned\n\n## Phase 3\n- connect mobile and desktop around the same intent model\n- let precision editing remain available without being the only path",
