        "markdown": "# Primitives Below The Waterline\n\nPrimitives still matter, but mostly beneath the waterline.\n\nThey improve:\n- generated graph quality\n- editable graph quality\n- composability\n- renderer consistency\n\nThey should serve intent-first graph creation, not replace it as the main experience.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
